      "text": "渴……渴极了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这句话我知道你是敢说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在，你还需要什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若有需要，只管说呀。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为何要如此折磨我？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你不敢说的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你需要的是什么……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你在想什么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才我假如走了，你是不是要发狂？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只是想不出你为什么要这样做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有，我一心想为你生个孩子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我们……我们……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我无法了解你的思想。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一心想瞧瞧，我们生下来的孩子，是怎么样的一个人，我真是想得要发疯，想得要死……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有了这样的孩子，你开不开心？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你叫我该说什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "将来怀念你，和现在杀死你，这完全是两回事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上除了你之外，只怕谁也不会认为这是两回事的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不是早已说过，我和别人不同么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我的确早已说过，你的确和别人不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "婚礼？……你还是要和快活王结婚？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认为不对？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "生孩子和嫁人，更是两回事了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你莫忘了，你是他的女儿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若不是他的女儿，我又怎会嫁给他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还有什么话要对我说？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还有什么话说？……一个女孩子能一面躺在我怀里，说她爱我，一面却又下手点我的穴道……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这样的女孩子，也不是人人都能遇得到的，你说是么……你本该觉得幸运才是，是么……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢谢你的关心，我会睡的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白宫主，白王妃，我不好，一点也不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不开心？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道就开心么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你那狠毒的心肠，我的确没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你无论有什么，我都不稀罕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么？你说是什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我还不能告诉你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？……为什么？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因我有的这件东西，正是和他共有的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好妹子，你仔细去想想吧，但愿你莫要想出来，否则……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七七，莫哭，你若哭，她就更得意了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但她……她和沈浪，莫非……莫非……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她和沈浪会怎样，你难道还不相信沈浪？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但她……这恶毒的女人，什么事都能做得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "傻孩子，她这样说，只不过是故意要来气你的，你怎可真的相信……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但说不定也是真的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是真的……不会是真的！",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若认为不会是真的，为何要哭？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王怜花，你为何要这样说？你为何要令她伤心？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过是在说真话而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我和她的确有许多相同之处，只除了一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她爱沈浪，而我却不。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因她不得不杀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这有两点原因：第一、是为了快活王，她想复仇，就只有嫁给快活王，她嫁给快活王就不能嫁给沈浪……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这简直不是人的脾气。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老天为什么要这样安排？……为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫要听他胡说八道！白飞飞的心事，他知道个屁。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我真不懂，老天为何要你们这两个人生出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因老天也想瞧瞧人间的这场好戏。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来三位还不知道……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们真的要成亲了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此大事，焉能说笑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明天……他们好快……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒当真是说打架就绕辫子。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢吉言……这位熊公子呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大红的？……你这不是要我的命！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，朱姑娘呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪选的是什么颜色？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下不知道。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 447,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎会不知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈公子的事，一向由白姑娘亲自料理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "过了明天，你我又将如何？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 457,
      "line_end": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "明天我就要成亲了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你心里有什么感觉？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些事，我要留到明天以后再去想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我毫无感觉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你已麻木了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 485,
      "line_end": 485
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "麻木的人，就没有痛苦；麻木的人，是有福的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "麻木了的人，哪里还有什么主意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你无论在打什么主意，都是没有用的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 503,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伟大",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看起来活脱脱就像我孙子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些天，你日子过得好么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 567,
      "line_end": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不理我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你为什么伤心？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 575,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我当然没有你那么开心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 577,
      "line_end": 577
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我开心？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 579,
      "line_end": 579
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有别人替你换衣服，有别人服侍你，你还不开心么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 581,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你又犯小心眼儿了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 585,
      "line_end": 585
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么总是相信别人的话？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 591,
      "line_end": 591
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不开心，怎么能笑得出？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 595,
      "line_end": 595
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的确有些开心，但却决不是为了你所说的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是为了什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 599,
      "line_end": 599
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在莫要问，不久你就会知道的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 601,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日想必忙坏你了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 617,
      "line_end": 617
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有事可忙，弟子反觉高兴。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 619,
      "line_end": 619
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "外面情况如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 621,
      "line_end": 621
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的不会有争杀之事么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 627,
      "line_end": 627
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来我今日大可一醉了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 633,
      "line_end": 633
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有我们四个客人么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 639,
      "line_end": 639
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林中除了四位外，还有谁配做王爷的嘉宾？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 641,
      "line_end": 641
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此说来，咱们倒该觉得荣幸得很了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 643,
      "line_end": 643
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 655,
      "line_end": 655
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子若是不说，那自然再好也没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 669,
      "line_end": 669
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王做了新郎官，还是像要找人打架似的……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 693,
      "line_end": 693
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒是实话。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 709,
      "line_end": 709
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是怎么回事，新娘子呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 717,
      "line_end": 717
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非临阵脱逃了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 719,
      "line_end": 719
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 725,
      "line_end": 725
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有些什么人在那里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 731,
      "line_end": 731
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那梳头师傅……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 737,
      "line_end": 737
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可曾仔细调查过他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 743,
      "line_end": 743
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷抬爱，弟子敢不全力以赴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 753,
      "line_end": 753
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好……很好……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 755,
      "line_end": 755
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但她此刻怎的还不来呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 757,
      "line_end": 757
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子方才已派人催驾了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 759,
      "line_end": 759
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你再去瞧瞧，那边是否有什么……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 761,
      "line_end": 761
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 763,
      "line_end": 763
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "新娘子来了，新郎官也不站起相迎么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 795,
      "line_end": 795
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正该如此。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 797,
      "line_end": 797
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家喝酒吧！只管尽兴。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 801,
      "line_end": 801
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样就算礼成了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 803,
      "line_end": 803
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢王爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 815,
      "line_end": 815
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这四位嘉宾，也不可无酒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 819,
      "line_end": 819
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "肩井",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 829,
      "line_end": 829
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "巅峰之后，佳境必下；极乐之欢，必不长久……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 851,
      "line_end": 851
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不生气？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 869,
      "line_end": 869
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "该……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 879,
      "line_end": 879
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "时机还未到来，我又有什么法子可想？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 887,
      "line_end": 887
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵是如此，也是无可奈何。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 893,
      "line_end": 893
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白飞飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，春宵一刻值千金，你的确该入洞房了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 925,
      "line_end": 925
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王怜花到底不愧为风流种子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 927,
      "line_end": 927
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人只怕本是在宫外巡逻的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 933,
      "line_end": 933
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 935,
      "line_end": 935
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞧他的神色，莫非已有变？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 937,
      "line_end": 937
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但愿如此……但愿如此……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 939,
      "line_end": 939
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贺喜？……本王今日婚典，你们已传出去了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 949,
      "line_end": 949
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喜讯绝未走漏出去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 951,
      "line_end": 951
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_xin_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方心骑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然绝未走漏，别人又怎会知道？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 953,
      "line_end": 953
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子愿领防护不严之罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 955,
      "line_end": 955
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这话也不差……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 965,
      "line_end": 965
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们一共来了多少人？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 967,
      "line_end": 967
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人看来是何模样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 973,
      "line_end": 973
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪，你瞧这卜公直是真的为了送礼来的么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 995,
      "line_end": 995
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕未必。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 997,
      "line_end": 997
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就凭卜公直这些人，岂非真的送礼来的么。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 999,
      "line_end": 999
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那也说不定。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1013,
      "line_end": 1013
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_gong_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜公直",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么神秘的武功？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1031,
      "line_end": 1031
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖中人言人殊，谁也说不清楚，但听来那像是一种巫术……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1033,
      "line_end": 1033
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这巫术最大的用处就是逃走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1035,
      "line_end": 1035
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "逃走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1037,
      "line_end": 1037
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_gong_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜公直",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "逃走，这倒有趣得很……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1043,
      "line_end": 1043
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_gong_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜公直",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南疆卜公直进见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1055,
      "line_end": 1055
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下远道而来，小王如何敢当。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1061,
      "line_end": 1061
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜官人说得太客气了，快请一旁宽坐。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1067,
      "line_end": 1067
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "劳动大驾，已不敢当，怎敢再受阁下的厚礼？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1073,
      "line_end": 1073
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然如此，小王只有生受了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 1081,
      "line_end": 1081
    }
